    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a87",
      "text": "[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a88",
      "text": "　久しぶりに[Oculus Quest 2]を起動したら段階的なシステムアップデートでみるみるバージョンが上がっていく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a89",
      "text": "　　v50台からv70、v200台、最終的に[Meta Horizon OS] v2.1になった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a8a",
      "text": "　[『三体』]1巻を読み切った",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a8b",
      "text": "　\tネタバレ踏む前に『三体』と『[プロジェクト・ヘイル・メアリー]』を読みたい所存",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a8c",
      "text": "　\t乙[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a8d",
      "text": "　\tプロヘメ、ネタバレがそこかしこに散らばっており危険[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c52200000000000a4a8e",
      "text": "　\t急がねば[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845539,
      "updated": 1777845539
    },
    {
